Description: Computer break timer for active minds 
 Brain Break is for people concerned about the mental and physical
 issues connected to long periods of computer use. It reminds you to
 take short, frequent breaks as well as longer rest breaks, and its
 unique design allows you to finish that "one last thing" without
 reaching for a postpone button.
